            img(src="images/thengine-share-1.jpg" alt="thengine's microinteractoin button in its normal state" title="Thengine Share Button 1")
          .medium-6.columns
            img(src="images/thengine-share-2.jpg" alt="thengine's microinteractoin button in its clicked state" title="Thengine Share Button 2")
        h3 The Outcome
        p After several phases of user testing and iteration, I received a final approval from Thengine's founders and passed along the front-end to be developed by a back-end team. 
        p The project was incredibly hard work but it was my first step into the world of UX and I am happy with how my process helped Thengine take thousands of concepts in boil them into one tangible idea that was usable on all devices.
        p Thengine's Ruby on Rails developers are hard and work and we should be able to see a public beta soon.